Finance & Accounting Assistant Job (Online E-commerce),
Jakarta, Indonesia
Responsibilities
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting on behalf of an established local online E-commerce provider. Our client offers online e-commerce and search engine for buying and selling product. Our client is seeking a professional finance & accounting person to fill the job of Finance & Accounting Assistant, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia. Key job responsibilities will include: Assisting of preparation monthly financial statements and analysis, and to ensure the Inter-Company transactions are recorded properlyCheck vendors’ invoices and record it for paymentsWork with other people internally to ensure that all costs are properly bookedManaging and reporting on all Petty Cash related transactionsTo file the documents systematicallyTo assist in preparing all necessary reports and schedule for statutory/ tax reportingTo highlight to management if any lapses and violations to the internal control, policies and procedures Job Requirements  Graduated from reputable university majoring in accountancy2 – 4 years accounting/ finance experience, from multinational companiesStrong understanding of accounting theory, organization, tracking, follow-up and analytical skiils with the ability to collect, access and report factual data and present logical conclusionsGood communication and interpersonal skiils to co-op with internal staff and third partiesGood problem solving with high team spirit to work with other staffAbility to write and speak in English is a mustProficient in Excel is required All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence. If you are a suitable match for this position please send your application to technology@monroeconsulting.com
